1. COMPILING in *NIX system
------------------------
aclocal
autoconf
libtoolize --force
automake --add-missing
./configure
make

INSTALL
--------
make install

UNINSTALL
---------
make uninstall

2. TO USE UNISEG WITH ANT
-------------------------

On Linux:
add "-DWITH_ANT_PLUGIN" in compiler option

or with automake
source ant/scrits/setuniseg.sh
then ant/configure